                    Imagine the Universe Theatre Archive

   Welcome to the Imagine the Universe! Theatre Archive, our collection of
     past feature movies at the virtual theater. In order to enjoy these
     productions, you will have to have the appropriate software on your
   computer. This software, for Macintosh and PC, can be obtained here at
                                 no charge!

                              Available movies:

    * The Dynamic X-ray Sky
    * They're Here, They're There, They're Everywhere! Gamma Ray Bursts!
    * What a Blast!
    * Star Life
    * Deploy, Deploy, Deploy!
    * Launch!
    * Supernova X-rays
    * X-ray Binaries
    * Look, There in the Sky!
    * Kepler's Laws I, II, and III
    * AXAF
    * Image This!

